    "In Panel B, the sample in Column 1 is at the group-round level (1400 rounds).",
    "The sample in Columns 2, 3, 4, 5 is at the participant-period level (5 participants × 1400 periods of each type).",
    "The sample in Columns 6 and 7 is at the group-period level (1400 periods of each type).",
    "Exploration= share of unknown mountains explored in the round; Individual payoff = participant-level period payoffs in Canadian dollars; I(Individual found max):0/1=1 if the location of the maximum was found by the participant in the period; I(Group found max):0/1=1 if the location of the maximum was found by at least one participant in the period.",
